{
  "stem": "11641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and the kapo-- there was a Jewish kapo-- who-- or a Jewish supervisor-- who beat you quite a while.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It did not happen to me, but I saw it happening.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a German master was over all you, and he was-- he was a master of life and death, also.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And on top of it, the commander of the camp was the famous Goeth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] how do you describe him?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Human hell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because no matter where you worked, you worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he was always going to the gun, and-- and-- and the German shepherd with you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you-- if you looked at him, he didn't let you look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just shot you, that's all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would let the dog run over you, without provocation, without anything, without ifs or buts.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, from our barracks, somebody ran away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took 10 people from the barracks at random, in the middle of the camp, and they shot them-- over the four who were running away.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The second time someone ran away, again, and they shot 20.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At random.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- in the meantime, I was with a friend of mine, also from Wisnicz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Abush Reich, was his name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, Abush, the law of averages are against us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, we have to get out of here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were walking one Sunday afternoon-- we had the free time only Sunday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were walking and we saw a big line over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we asked-- in the camp itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, I heard the whole Bochnia ghetto is liquidated.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's nobody left there-- in ghetto B.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the total ghetto, the total ghetto B is being liquidated.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
